---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service" description="Terms of service for EvanTools. Read the conditions for using our free online download tools." noindex={true}>
	<section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">
		<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
		<div class="prose max-w-none text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-6">
			<p><strong>Last updated:</strong> March 26, 2026</p>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Acceptance of Terms</h2>
			<p>By accessing or using this website and its tools, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, please do not use our services.</p>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Service Description</h2>
			<p>Our tools allow you to download publicly available content from social media platforms. The service is provided "as is" and "as available" without warranties of any kind, either express or implied.</p>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Permitted Use</h2>
			<p>You may only use our tools to download content that is publicly accessible. You are solely responsible for ensuring that your use of downloaded content complies with applicable laws and the terms of service of the originating platform.</p>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Copyright and Intellectual Property</h2>
			<p>All content downloaded through our tools belongs to its respective creators and copyright holders. You must respect copyright laws and obtain proper authorization before redistributing, modifying, or using downloaded content for commercial purposes.</p>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Prohibited Activities</h2>
			<p>You may not use our tools to: download private or restricted content without authorization; infringe upon the intellectual property rights of others; engage in any activity that violates applicable laws or regulations; or attempt to disrupt, overload, or interfere with the operation of our services.</p>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Limitation of Liability</h2>
			<p>We are not liable for any damages arising from your use of our tools, including but not limited to direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages. We are not responsible for the content you download or how you use it.</p>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Service Availability</h2>
			<p>We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue the service at any time without prior notice. We do not guarantee uninterrupted or error-free operation of our tools.</p>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Changes to These Terms</h2>
			<p>We may revise these Terms of Service at any time. Continued use of the service after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
